        "name": "Numerical code verification acceptance criteria — MRL 2",
        "description": "Solver passes published benchmark suite (FDA nozzle, lid-driven cavity) with observed order of accuracy within 10% of theoretical. No code modifications applied."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verification benchmarks (FDA nozzle and lid-driven cavity) demonstrate observed order of accuracy of 1.87 vs. theoretical 2.0 for the second-order upwind scheme — within the 10% tolerance. No user-defined functions or code modifications were applied, so code verification is inherited from the vendor qualification package."
    },
    {
