      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU because the Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes turbulence closure (SST k-ω) has been validated for internal rotating flows in the published FDA critical path study under comparable Re and geometry. A formal model form assessment would be required at MRL 3 or above."
    },
