      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Model inputs uncertainty is scoped out at MRL 2 because all boundary condition values are derived from NIST-traceable measurements with reported uncertainty (covered under the Test conditions factor). A full parametric uncertainty propagation study is deferred to MRL 3 submissions."
