      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test samples is scoped out at MRL 2 because the validation experiments use a single FDA GCBP specimen manufactured to the nominal CAD geometry. Part-to-part variability assessment is not required at MRL 2 for a Class II device where the predicate comparison is geometry-normalised."
